@Node MAIN "A Guide to the Star Wars Universe - fusion furnace"

* The fusion furnace power-generating device produces heat and light, and
serves as the power source for recharging the energy cells of vehicles,
droids, and weapons. These furnaces range in size from huge spaceport models
for powering capital ships to small, portable models for recharging energy
cells on the move.

